{"data":[{"date":"09:07 21/08","title":"\u0110T n\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Asiad d\u00f9 tr\u1eafng tay \u1edf b\u1ea3ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/dt-nu-thai-lan-vao-tu-ket-asiad-du-trang-tay-o-bang-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ed9t c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 trong m\u01a1 m\u1edbi x\u1ea3y ra \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1edbi \u0110T n\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan khi h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.</h2><h2>\u0110T n\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Asiad d\u00f9 b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng C</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e1 th\u0103m may r\u1ee7i \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T n\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 n\u1eef Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD 2018. \u1ede ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u1ec3 thua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 ch\u00f9a V\u00e0ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u00eam th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd x\u1ebfp cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng C khi kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i \u1edf m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef, b\u1edfi \u0110T n\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 1 trong 2 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T n\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Asiad d\u00f9 tr\u1eafng tay \u1edf b\u1ea3ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T n\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Asiad d\u00f9 tr\u1eafng tay \u1edf b\u1ea3ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/DT-nu-Thai-Lan-vao-tu-ket-Asiad-du-trang-tay-o-bang-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T n\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf ASIAD 2018 khi l\u00e0 1 trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef, do ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 11 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tham d\u1ef1 n\u00ean gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia l\u00e0m 3 b\u1ea3ng, 2 b\u1ea3ng A, B c\u00f3 4 \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng C ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 \u0111\u1ed9i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp th\u00ec 2 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t - nh\u00ec m\u1ed7i b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 ba c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch cao s\u1ebd v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Theo quy ch\u1ebf gi\u1ea3i, khi ph\u00e2n h\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 ba, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c n\u1eef Hong Kong thua Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-8, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9m Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 ch\u00f9a V\u00e0ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, t\u1edd Siam Sports (Th\u00e1i Lan) \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eadt t\u00edt: \"0 \u0111i\u1ec3m, Th\u00e1i Lan v\u1eabn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp\". Tuy nhi\u00ean kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i s\u00e2u v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng cao khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Trung Qu\u1ed1c ho\u1eb7c Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"nu viet nam\" title=\"n\u1eef vi\u1ec7t nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/500-3-1534682271-825-width500height333.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ni\u1ec1m vui c\u1ee7a \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i 'k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch' Th\u00e1i Lan</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng C v\u1edbi n\u1eef Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o l\u00fac 15h00 chi\u1ec1u nay 21/8. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c thua xa tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00e1c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng C. Khi \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng A t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/nu-viet-nam-vs-nu-thai-lan-asiad-2018-372-194816.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/500-3-1534682271-825-width500height333.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/nu-viet-nam-vs-nu-thai-lan-asiad-2018-372-194816.html\">N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-2 N\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan (KT): \u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan b\u1ea3ng C...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5722","checkdouble":"194956"},{"date":"09:37 21/08","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-nuoi-vi-chan-thuong-cua-do-hung-dung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng trong ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf ASIAD.</h2><h2>HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/chan-thuong-cua-hung-dung-khong-can-phau-thuat.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf n\u1eeda cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t n\u00e0y, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi m\u1ea5t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t n\u00e0y: &ldquo;20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0ng qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n khi D\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u00f4ng Park v\u1eabn kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd trao cho anh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi D\u0169ng v\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n v\u1ec1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1edbm hay \u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd do D\u0169ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh. C\u00f2n t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean D\u0169ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n th\u1ea5y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i AFF Suzuki Cup cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay&rdquo;.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft c\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb s\u1ef1 nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;Th\u1eadt ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Anh em \u0111ang ch\u01a1i v\u00e0o phom th\u00ec em \u1ea5y l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u&rdquo;, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft chia s\u1ebb \u0111\u1ea7y ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t t\u1eeb 4-6 tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t to l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u0169ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y khi V-League tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 9 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-nu-thai-lan-vao-tu-ket-asiad-du-trang-tay-o-bang-viet-nam-168-194956.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/dt-nu-thai-lan-vao-tu-ket-asiad-du-trang-tay-o-bang-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-nu-thai-lan-vao-tu-ket-asiad-du-trang-tay-o-bang-viet-nam-168-194956.html\">\u0110T n\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Asiad d\u00f9 tr\u1eafng tay \u1edf b\u1ea3ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br />\r\nM\u1ed9t c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 trong m\u01a1 m\u1edbi x\u1ea3y ra \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1edbi \u0110T n\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan khi h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194953.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194953.html\">HLV Bahrain n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Bahrain \u00f4ng Samir Chammam cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u g\u00ec v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5721","checkdouble":"194960"},{"date":"10:15 21/08","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/vff5479-15341729950901227889727.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c gi\u00fap c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi 3 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pakistan, Nepal v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua. Ngo\u00e0i y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t cao c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u0103ng hoa.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/vff5479-15341729950901227889727.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Park Hang Seo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, HLV Park Hang Seo chia s\u1ebb: \u201cC\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft g\u00ec \u0111\u00e2u. T\u00f4i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng m\u1edf l\u00f2ng v\u00e0 th\u1eadt th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. T\u00f4i nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i b\u1edfi s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i th\u00ec s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec. D\u00f9 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i l\u00fac t\u00f4i h\u01a1i lo l\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ko \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 v\u1ec1 tinh th\u1ea7n Vi\u1ec7t Nam, s\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft, quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft. \u0110\u00e3 l\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i hay th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua nhi\u1ec1u th\u0103ng tr\u1ea7m n\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb b\u1ecf m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eadp trung, nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau xa h\u01a1n \u1edf ASIAD 18.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng sau khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y b\u1ecb g\u00e3y ng\u00f3n ch\u00e2n c\u00e1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u00f4ng Park c\u0169ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng 19 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1 thay ph\u1ea7n H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 ng\u00e0y 23 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 g\u1eb7p Bahrain. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c l\u1eabn kinh nghi\u1ec7m, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-nuoi-vi-chan-thuong-cua-do-hung-dung-168-194960.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-nuoi-vi-chan-thuong-cua-do-hung-dung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-nuoi-vi-chan-thuong-cua-do-hung-dung-168-194960.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng trong...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-nu-thai-lan-vao-tu-ket-asiad-du-trang-tay-o-bang-viet-nam-168-194956.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/dt-nu-thai-lan-vao-tu-ket-asiad-du-trang-tay-o-bang-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-nu-thai-lan-vao-tu-ket-asiad-du-trang-tay-o-bang-viet-nam-168-194956.html\">\u0110T n\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Asiad d\u00f9 tr\u1eafng tay \u1edf b\u1ea3ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 trong m\u01a1 m\u1edbi x\u1ea3y ra \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1edbi \u0110T n\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan khi h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194953.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194953.html\">HLV Bahrain n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Bahrain \u00f4ng Samir Chammam cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u g\u00ec v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5720","checkdouble":"194961"},{"date":"10:29 21/08","title":"N\u00f3ng: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00ean s\u00f3ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/19/lo-dien-don-vi-nam-ban-quyen-phat-song-asiad-2018-tai-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00e0i Ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i Vi\u1ec7t Nam VOV s\u1eafp tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u1eafm b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 r\u1ebb.</h2><h2>VOV s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Zing, T\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c VOV, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ebf K\u1ef7 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018. VOV v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n xong v\u1edbi KJSM World Corp v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn ch\u1ed1t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u1eafm b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u1eafm b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/lo-dien-don-vi-nam-ban-quyen-phat-song-asiad-2018-tai-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>VOV s\u1eafp tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh\u00a0\u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u1eafm b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u00e1c cho bi\u1ebft m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 VOV chi ra \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 1.7 tri\u1ec7u USD (x\u1ea5p x\u1ec9 39.5 t\u1ec9 VN\u0110). M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 r\u1ebb so v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 4 tri\u1ec7u USD m\u00e0 VTV cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0a ra khi\u1ebfn hai b\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua ASIAD 2018 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu th\u00f4ng tin VOV \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain tr\u00ean s\u00f3ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, c\u00e1c m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Vi\u1ec7t Nam tranh t\u00e0i c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfu r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>K\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e0i n\u00e0o \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018 khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i theo d\u00f5i di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u qua c\u00e1c k\u00eanh chi\u1ebfu \"l\u1eadu\". \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thu h\u00fat nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi quan t\u00e2m h\u01a1n c\u1ea3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \"chui\" l\u00e0m d\u1ea5y l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u tranh c\u00e3i. Ph\u00eda VTV \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i r\u1eb1ng v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c ra gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i xem \"chui\" l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, vi\u1ec7c xem qua c\u00e1c k\u00eanh kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ebfng n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i ho\u1eb7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn NHM m\u1ea5t h\u1ee9ng ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o. N\u1ebfu VOV c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfu ASIAD 2018 r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i tr\u00ean s\u00f3ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-thanh-cong-cung-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194961.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-nuoi-vi-chan-thuong-cua-do-hung-dung-168-194960.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-nu-thai-lan-vao-tu-ket-asiad-du-trang-tay-o-bang-viet-nam-168-194956.html\">\u0110T n\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Asiad d\u00f9 tr\u1eafng tay \u1edf b\u1ea3ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194953.html\">HLV Bahrain n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-asiad-2018-ngay-hom-nay-218-cua-doan-ttvn-472-194942.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ASIAD 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 21/8 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bac-si-cua-olympic-viet-nam-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-xuan-truong-ngoi-du-bi-168-194910.html\">B\u00e1c s\u0129 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5719","checkdouble":"194963"},{"date":"09:07 21/08","title":"Carragher: \"Van Dijk s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Liverpool\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/carragher-van-dijk-se-tro-thanh-huyen-thoai-cua-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jamie Carragher cho r\u1eb1ng trung v\u1ec7 Van Dijk c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i Liverpool sau khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1ee9c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng trong th\u1eddi gian qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Van Dijk \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/video-tong-hop-crystal-palace-02-liverpool-vong-2-premier-league-201819-326-194945.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Crystal Palace</span> \u0111\u00eam qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 chi ra 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Van Dijk t\u1eeb Southampton v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t. V\u00e0 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 H\u00e0 Lan \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, qua \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Carragher khen ng\u1ee3i Van Dijk h\u1ebft l\u1eddi sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Palace h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Carragher khen ng\u1ee3i Van Dijk h\u1ebft l\u1eddi sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Palace h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/carragher-van-dijk-se-tro-thanh-huyen-thoai-cua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Carragher khen ng\u1ee3i Van Dijk sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Crystal Palace</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nJamie Carragher \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khen ng\u1ee3i Van Dijk sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi d\u1ea5u v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i bi\u1ebft Van Dijk l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i ngh\u0129. Ch\u00fang ta lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng Liverpool kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u00ec h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i. Nh\u01b0ng b\u00e2y gi\u1edd h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Van Dijk, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 t\u00f4i cho l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Van Dijk l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Vincent Kompany \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ea1i Man City. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 huy v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u n\u00e9t gi\u1ed1ng nhau. Khi Kompany \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec9nh cao phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 3 n\u0103m, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n anh \u1ea5y n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTrong 3 \u0111\u1ebfn 4 n\u0103m t\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League hay Champions League th\u00ec t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Van Dijk c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Alan Hansen khi ch\u00fang ta n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Liverpool. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Van Dijk nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u1ea3i gi\u00fap Liverpool gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn. Khi \u0111\u00f3, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1edb \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi t\u00ean v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5718","checkdouble":"194955"},{"date":"09:27 21/08","title":"Mourinho y\u00eau c\u1ea7u MU b\u00e1n Martial trong 1 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/mourinho-yeu-cau-mu-ban-martial-trong-1-tuan-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Ed Woodward b\u00e1n sao tr\u1ebb Martial tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda.</h2><h2>Martial ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho y\u00eau c\u1ea7u MU b\u00e1n Martial trong 1 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho y\u00eau c\u1ea7u MU b\u00e1n Martial trong 1 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/mourinho-yeu-cau-mu-ban-martial-trong-1-tuan-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Anthony Martial g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn h\u01a1n qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e8 n\u00e0y sau khi g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu cho Mourinho. Anh r\u1eddi tour du \u0111\u1ea5u M\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a MU t\u1eeb s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ee9a con th\u1ee9 hai ra \u0111\u1eddi. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00f3i l\u00e0 Martial \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 Carrington b\u00e1o danh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu khi Martial kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 tr\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edbm h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 trong m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/martial-bi-phat-nang-vi-bo-tap-chong-doi-mourinho-172-192498.html\" target=\"_blank\">chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 c\u00f3 \u00fap m\u1edf vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea1t Martial 2 tu\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u01a1ng</span>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMartial ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton khi Alexis Sanchez b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nh\u01b0ng Martial \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc The Seagulls v\u00e0 b\u1ecb r\u00fat ra kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n sau 1 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho y\u00eau c\u1ea7u MU b\u00e1n Martial</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Brighton k\u1ebft th\u00fac, t\u1edd Daily Star \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra y\u00eau c\u1ea7u bu\u1ed9c gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Ed Woodward ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n Martial.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 cho r\u1eb1ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Martial kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea7n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y ti\u1ec1n chi ti\u00eau trong th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton, HLV Sam Allardyce \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t r\u1eb1ng Martial kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cMartial kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i cho Man United. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 nh\u01b0ng Man United \u0111\u00e3 mua nh\u1ea7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ea5t r\u1ed3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u00e0 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1 kh\u1ea9m h\u01a1n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 bao. \u0110\u00e1ng l\u1ebd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. \u0110\u00e1ng l\u1ebd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 Leroy Sane. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Mourinho\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/victor-lindelof-bat-ngo-tho-lo-uoc-mo-khong-the-tin-duoc-172-194938.html\">Victor Lindelof b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u1ed5 l\u1ed9 \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-can-co-trach-nhiem-voi-ke-hoach-mua-sam-cua-minh-172-194925.html\">Mourinho c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5717","checkdouble":"194957"},{"date":"10:07 21/08","title":"HLV Klopp n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \"tr\u1ea3m\" Fabinho","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/21/hlv-klopp-noi-gi-sau-khi-tiep-tuc-tram-fabinho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Klopp x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng t\u00e2n binh Fabinho b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Liverpool \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Palace v\u00ec l\u00fd do chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 chi ra h\u01a1n 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Fabinho t\u1eeb Monaco h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V Liverpool k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Selhurst Park \u0111\u00eam qua. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Fabinho l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong danh s\u00e1ch 18 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Crystal Palace.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u1ea3m Fabinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u1ea3m Fabinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/hlv-klopp-noi-gi-sau-khi-tiep-tuc-tram-fabinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Fabinho b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra, Klopp chia s\u1ebb: <strong>\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y qua tu\u1ea7n kh\u00e1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u1edbi Fabinho. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf Liverpool trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a West Ham, Fabinho \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng anh hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Anfield.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cKhi t\u00f4i t\u1edbi Liverpool, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ed1t cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t. Trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n giao h\u1eefu, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c nhau. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1eady n\u00ean nh\u00ecn chung t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Crystal Palace, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p West Ham. C\u00f3 v\u1ebb c\u1ed7 m\u00e1y c\u1ee7a Klopp \u0111ang ch\u1ea1y t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0o, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-crystal-palace-02-liverpool-172-194948.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lien-tuc-toa-sang-mo-salah-van-bi-thay-che-172-194946.html\">Li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, Mo Salah v\u1eabn b\u1ecb th\u1ea7y ch\u00ea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5716","checkdouble":"194962"},{"date":"08:43 21/08","title":"HLV Bahrain n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/21/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Bahrain \u00f4ng Samir Chammam cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u g\u00ec v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><h2>HLV Bahrain kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1\u00a0\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Bahrain ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-2 qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i 20/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV \u0111\u1ed9i Bahrain \u00f4ng Samir Chammam \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, song v\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra lo \u00e2u khi ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Bahrain kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Bahrain kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/089549700_1524748953-20180426_150959.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Olympic Bahrain th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb: \u201cN\u00f3i chung t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Bahrain \u0111\u1ebfn ASIAD 2018 v\u1edbi t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Trong tay t\u00f4i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110a ph\u1ea7n h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i sinh n\u0103m 1997, 1998. C\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n sinh n\u0103m 1999 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi sinh n\u0103m 2000. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 Olympic Tokyo 2020 v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ch\u00fa t\u00e2m v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f3\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 8 n\u0103m, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Bahrain t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD. Khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-1, sau c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 Thanh Trung. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain c\u0169ng gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 ASIAD. \u0110i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e1c th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 \u2018\u0111\u00e0n anh\u2019 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra 19 gi\u1edd 30 ng\u00e0y 23/8 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Patriot Patriot Candrabhaga, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Bekasi, t\u1ec9nh T\u00e2y Java. M\u1eddi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bac-si-cua-olympic-viet-nam-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-xuan-truong-ngoi-du-bi-168-194910.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/bac-si-cua-olympic-viet-nam-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-xuan-truong-ngoi-du-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bac-si-cua-olympic-viet-nam-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-xuan-truong-ngoi-du-bi-168-194910.html\">B\u00e1c s\u0129 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, b\u00e1c s\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam Tr\u1ea7n Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/toi-do-cua-nhat-ban-an-tuong-voi-toc-do-cua-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam-168-194906.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/toi-do-cua-nhat-ban-an-tuong-voi-toc-do-cua-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/toi-do-cua-nhat-ban-an-tuong-voi-toc-do-cua-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam-168-194906.html\">T\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br />\r\nTrao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Yuta Kamiya - ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Hoa anh \u0111\u00e0o \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tro-ly-than-can-cua-hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-ha-nhat-ban-168-194894.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/tro-ly-than-can-cua-hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-ha-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tro-ly-than-can-cua-hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-ha-nhat-ban-168-194894.html\">Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd th\u00e2n c\u1eadn c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft h\u1ea1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br />\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd th\u00e2n c\u1eadn c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5715","checkdouble":"194953"},{"date":"07:57 21/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 21/8: Barca \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3n Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/1/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-218-barca-dinh-ngay-don-pogba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 21/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Real t\u00ednh \"\u0111\u00e1nh \u00fap\" sao tr\u1ebb Dortmund.</strong> Real Madrid \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Julian Weigl c\u1ee7a Borussia Dortmund. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 'Sergio Busquets m\u1edbi', Weigl s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Los Blancos m\u1ea5t \u0111i s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 75 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Barca t\u00ednh \u0111\u00f3n Pogba v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1. </strong>T\u1edd Don Balon \u0111\u01b0a tin, Barcelona s\u1ebd ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i Paul Pogba t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m sau thay v\u00ec ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. M\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Pogba v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c M.U ch\u01b0a b\u00e1n anh ngay \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 v\u00ec h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 218 Barca \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3n Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 218 Barca \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3n Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-188-pogba-duoc-thuong-lon-neu-tu-choi-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pogba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Barca v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 t\u1edbi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\"Harry Maguire \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf MU\". </strong>Jonny Evans ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Harry Maguire, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Leicester City. C\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Man United kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1 cho nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 m\u00ecnh t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nV\u00ec Karius su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Alisson. </strong>Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi v\u00e0 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Loris Karius. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, c\u1ef1u HLV Dortmund \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Arsenal nh\u1eafm trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga.</strong> Theo Daily Mirror, Arsenal mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga Igor Diveev c\u1ee7a Ufa. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u khi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o U20 Nga v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1eed tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn x\u1ee9 b\u1ea1ch d\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Firmino cung khong chiu kem canh voi thanh tich tuong tu Salah\" title=\"Firmino c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu k\u00e9m c\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 Salah\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/25/roberto-firmino-day-la-mua-giai-tot-nhat-trong-su-nghiep-cua-toi.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Firmino mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool l\u00e2u d\u00e0i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Firmino mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.</strong> Trong kho\u1ea3ng 1 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng tin Roberto Firmino \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barcelona \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai l\u00e2u d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a anh n\u1eb1m \u1edf Liverpool khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Dortmund nh\u1eafm \"h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\" Barca. </strong>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Barcelona, Paco Alcacer \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Borussia Dortmund xem l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb gi\u1edd t\u1edbi h\u1ebft k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5714","checkdouble":"194949"},{"date":"07:15 21/08","title":"Li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, Mo Salah v\u1eabn b\u1ecb th\u1ea7y ch\u00ea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/lien-tuc-toa-sang-mo-salah-van-bi-thay-che.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mohamed Salah \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 c\u1ee7a Liverpool tr\u01b0\u1edbc Crystal Palace. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah v\u1eabn d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam kh\u1eafc cho h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Salah th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n Premier League, Mohamed Salah \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap Liverpool v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua West Ham 4-0. L\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Crystal Palace \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp c\u00f2n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n th\u1ebf. Anh tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 The Kop c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Salah ki\u1ebfm v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty \u0111\u1ec3 James Milner th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ph\u00fat 45. T\u1edbi ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd th\u1ee9 3, l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 11 c\u1ee7a Liverpool c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 Sadio Mane \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam kh\u1eafc h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam kh\u1eafc h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Salah-bi-Klopp-che.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam kh\u1eafc</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh Salah l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf cho Liverpool. T\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha b\u1ee9t \u0111i nhanh nh\u1eb9n, anh bu\u1ed9c Aaron Wan-Bissaka ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh s\u00e1t v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m v\u00e0 b\u1ecb tru\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Klopp ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Liverpool, Salah v\u1eabn b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn. \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 c\u00fa l\u1ed1p b\u00f3ng v\u1ecdt x\u00e0 sau \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Naby Keita. V\u00e0 HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah v\u1eabn b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, nh\u01b0ng Mo Salah c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng&rdquo;, Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. &ldquo;D\u00f9 sao, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p trong c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;X\u00e9t tr\u00ean kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Salah ph\u1ea3i tham gia nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 7 t\u1edbi, Liverpool s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Brighton t\u1edbi s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 3 Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool (V\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19):<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279653\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/8/21/liverpool-crystal-palace-100554359_1200_96.mp4&amp;autoplay=false&amp;urlParent=http://bongdanet.vn/video/crystal-palace-0-2-liverpool-premier-league-ngoai-hang-anh-vong-2-tbd71154\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5713","checkdouble":"194946"},{"date":"07:36 21/08","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/21/de-bruyne-len-tieng-ve-chan-thuong-mat-nua-mua-giai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n- T\u00ednh c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool, Sadio Mane \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 8 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palace, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n&emsp;<br>\r\n- Liverpool gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 34 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 2, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Man United (43) v\u00e0 Arsenal (36) l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Sadio-Mane-ghi-ban-cho-Liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Sadio Mane \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n- Liverpool ch\u1ec9 thua 1 sau 10 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua t\u1ea1i Premier League, th\u1eafng 6 v\u00e0 h\u00f2a 3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Palace \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 16 sau 20 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thu\u1ed9c nh\u00f3m &ldquo;Big Six&rdquo; t\u1edbi s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 (h\u00f2a 2).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Roy Hodgson ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 100 t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng (th\u1eafng 87, h\u00f2a 65).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Wan-Bissaka \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Palace nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf t\u1ea1i Premier League (20 tu\u1ed5i, 267 ng\u00e0y).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- James Milner \u0111\u00e3 n\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh (48 tr\u1eadn, th\u1eafng 38 v\u00e0 h\u00f2a 10).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Milner \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf 13 trong s\u1ed1 15 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Premier League, 9 cho Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ghi 8 b\u00e0n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Premier League \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m 11m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool (V\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19):<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279653\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/8/21/liverpool-crystal-palace-100554359_1200_96.mp4&amp;autoplay=false&amp;urlParent=http://bongdanet.vn/video/crystal-palace-0-2-liverpool-premier-league-ngoai-hang-anh-vong-2-tbd71154\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5712","checkdouble":"194948"},{"date":"19:24 20/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 20/08: Mourinho s\u1ebd b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Gi\u00e1ng sinh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-2008-mourinho-se-bi-sa-thai-truoc-giang-sinh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 20/08.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho s\u1ebd b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Gi\u00e1ng sinh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 2008 MU c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 2008 MU c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/hlv-ky-cuu-ly-giai-tai-sao-mu-khong-ung-ho-mourinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho s\u1ebd b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Gi\u00e1ng sinh n\u1ebfu M.U ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i b\u1ebft b\u00e1t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Lee Sharpe, n\u1ebfu M.U ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn thua Brighton HLV Jose Mourinho s\u1ebd b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Gi\u00e1ng sinh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1eafm Falcao</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, Falcao c\u1ee7a Monaco l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Los Blancos nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi. Real ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 30 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>V\u00ec Chelsea, HLV Sarri nguy\u1ec7n b\u1ecf thu\u1ed1c l\u00e1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea sau 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Premier League. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111ang d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh ng\u1eebng h\u00fat thu\u1ed1c l\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 to\u00e0n t\u00e2m d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-maurizio-sarri-phat-bieu-ve-chelsea-172-194915.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/hlv-maurizio-sarri-phat-bieu-ve-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-maurizio-sarri-phat-bieu-ve-chelsea-172-194915.html\">V\u00ec Chelsea, HLV Sarri nguy\u1ec7n b\u1ecf thu\u1ed1c l\u00e1</span><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea sau 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Premier League. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111ang d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh ng\u1eebng h\u00fat thu\u1ed1c l\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Firmino n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Firmino\" title=\"Firmino\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/firmino-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-dau-quan-cho-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Firmino cam k\u1ebft g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Firmino kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool l\u00e2u d\u00e0i thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c bu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb Aaron Ramsey</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Andrew Robertson s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Andrew Robertson, \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid s\u1eafp chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid ha Getafe 2-0\" title=\"Real Madrid ha Getafe 2-0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/goc-nhin-khong-ronaldo-real-madrid-con-vung-vang-hon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real s\u1eafp chi \u0111\u1eadm n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong 2 tu\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Man City l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch &quot;tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n&quot; John Stones</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan City mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi John Stones, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-len-ke-hoach-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-john-stones-172-194898.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/man-city-len-ke-hoach-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-john-stones.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-len-ke-hoach-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-john-stones-172-194898.html\">Man City l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t</span><br>\r\nMan City mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi John Stones, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Berbatov l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u1ea5n an C\u0110V MU sau tr\u1eadn thua Brighton</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Dimitar Berbatov cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c C\u0110V MU kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5711","checkdouble":"194926"},{"date":"21:28 20/08","title":"C\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 Top 10 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m c\u1ee7a UEFA","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/cong-bo-top-10-ung-vien-cho-giai-thuong-cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-nam-cua-uefa.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Top 10 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t  n\u0103m 2018 c\u1ee7a UEFA \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1, trong danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y bao g\u1ed3m to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong n\u0103m qua.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Top 10 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t\u00a0 n\u0103m 2018 c\u1ee7a UEFA ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, danh s\u00e1ch 10 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2018 c\u1ee7a UEFA ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n. Trong danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y bao g\u1ed3m to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong n\u0103m qua.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"10 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean danh hi\u1ec7u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2018 c\u1ee7a UEFA  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"10 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean danh hi\u1ec7u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2018 c\u1ee7a UEFA  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/cong-bo-top-10-ung-vien-cho-giai-thuong-cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-nam-cua-uefa.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo, Salah v\u00e0 Modric l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a n\u0103m c\u1ee7a UEFA</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2018 c\u1ee7a UEFA. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 ghi 15 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 13 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Champions League gi\u00fap Real l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Ronaldo c\u00f2n ghi 26 b\u00e0n sau 27 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf La Liga, t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMohamed Salah l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Ronaldo trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2018 c\u1ee7a UEFA. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i anh ghi 44 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn gi\u00fap Liverpool v\u00e0o Top 4 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u00c1 qu\u00e2n Champions League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSalah c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 gi\u00fap Ai C\u1eadp c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf VCK, nh\u01b0ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga anh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLuka Modric t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong danh s\u00e1ch \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho danh hi\u1ec7u cao qu\u00fd n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAntoine Griezmann, Lionel Messi, Kylian Mbappe, Kevin De Bruyne Raphael Varane, Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Sergio Ramos l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2018 c\u1ee7a UEFA.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m c\u1ee7a UEFA \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2011, ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u00e0 Messi, nh\u1eefng n\u0103m ti\u1ebfp theo Andres Iniesta (2012), Franck Ribery (2013), Ronaldo (2014), Messi (2015), Ronaldo (2016) v\u00e0 Ronaldo (2017) l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2018 c\u1ee7a UEFA s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 30 th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5710","checkdouble":"194930"}]}